Pine

It is pretty much just a green theme, what else can I say! The colors were taken from a friends JB setup and I might also make a light mode variant some time soon when I feel like it, it will also have a different color scheme. This theme will probably be more appealing to some and some not so much, but anyways I hope you like it!
